<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Oh, send out your light and your truth, let them lead me.</para>

<para style="q1">Let them bring me to your holy hill</para>

<para style="q1">and to your dwelling.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Then I will go to the altar of God,</para>

<para style="q1">to God my exceeding joy.</para>

<para style="q1">I will praise you with the harp, God, my God.</para>
